                            <li><span>Unwelcome comments:</span> Regarding a person’s lifestyle choices and practices, including those related to food, health, parenting, drugs, and employment.</li>
                            
                            
                            <li><span>Deliberate misgendering</span> or use of ‘dead’ or rejected names</li>
                            
                            <li><span>Displaying sexual images</span> or behavior</li>
                            
